data.description: Nice 4BR/2BA Brick home in North Macon, this home features a spacious floor plan with remodeled kitchen. The floors have been restored to its beautiful original hardwood flooring. Primary bedroom has a separate bath.  The garage has been closed in and is heated and cooled for a nice additional living space for den or playroom. The home is in a great location that is convenient to most everything, shopping, restaurants and I 75, Very easy commute to downtown Macon or to ATL.  Call today!
